item.title: Item checked utility link broken
item.content:encoded: I've been trying for a few days now and the item checker link under the utilities dropdown is broken. I'm not sure if it's on their end since I tried pulling up a cached version of the page and it went to some German student page that was written in German, or if it's on your end though.
